<section class="about-us">
  <div class="hero-banner">
    <div class="hero-banner-content">
      <h1 class="text-white">About Us</h1>
      <p>
        Discover our commitment to delivering the most accurate and
        comprehensive car specifications worldwide.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="container pt-100 px-80">
    <div class="section">
      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>
        At <%= memories.site_name %>, our mission is to be the ultimate resource
        for automotive enthusiasts, buyers, and industry professionals seeking
        detailed and reliable vehicle specifications. We strive to provide
        up-to-date and precise information on cars from every corner of the
        globe, helping you make informed decisions whether you’re buying,
        selling, or simply exploring various vehicle models.
      </p>
      <p>
        We understand that the world of automobiles is ever-evolving, and our
        goal is to stay ahead of industry trends by continually updating our
        database with the latest specifications, features, and reviews. Our
        commitment is to deliver not just data, but valuable insights that can
        guide you in your automotive journey.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>Our Values</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Accuracy:</strong> We are dedicated to providing the most
          precise and reliable specifications available. Our team meticulously
          verifies all data to ensure accuracy.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Comprehensiveness:</strong> Our database covers a wide range
          of vehicles, from the latest models to classic cars, providing
          exhaustive details to cater to every automotive need.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Transparency:</strong> We believe in clear and honest
          presentation of information. Our goal is to make it easy for you to
          find and understand vehicle specifications without any hidden agendas.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Innovation:</strong> Embracing technological advancements, we
          continuously improve our platform to enhance user experience and
          expand our data coverage.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Passion for Cars:</strong> Our love for automobiles drives us
          to bring the best and most accurate information to our users. We’re
          not just a database—we’re car enthusiasts dedicated to sharing our
          passion.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Customer Focus:</strong> We prioritize your needs and
          feedback, striving to improve our services based on what matters most
          to you, the automotive community.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>Our History</h2>
      <p>
        <%= memories.site_name %> was founded in 2024 with the vision of
        creating a comprehensive and user-friendly platform for automotive
        specifications. Our journey began with a small team of passionate
        automotive experts who saw a gap in the market for reliable and detailed
        vehicle data.
      </p>
      <p>
        Initially, we focused on gathering specifications for popular car
        models, but our vision quickly expanded to include a wider array of
        vehicles from various manufacturers worldwide. We invested in advanced
        data collection methods and built partnerships with automotive industry
        insiders to ensure the accuracy and relevance of our information.
      </p>
      <p>
        Over the years, <%= memories.site_name %> has grown significantly,
        expanding our database to cover over <%= memories.total_car %> of car,
        from contemporary releases to historical classics. We’ve introduced
        features such as interactive comparison tools and in-depth reviews,
        continuously enhancing the value we provide to our users.
      </p>
      <p>
        We have also celebrated several key milestones, including being
        recognized as a leading source of automotive specifications by industry
        publications. Our commitment to innovation and excellence remains at the
        core of our mission, and we are excited to continue evolving with the
        automotive landscape.
      </p>
      <p>
        As we look to the future, we aim to further expand our database,
        integrate cutting-edge technologies, and continue providing unparalleled
        service to our community. Thank you for being a part of our journey!
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
